INSERT INTO `oc_blog_article_description` VALUES (14,2,'P2P牵手珠宝商玩跨界O2O 布局线下消费','','','','&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin: 8.4pt 0cm 7.8pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 16.8pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt&quot;&gt;跨界已成为当下&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;P2P&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:\r\n9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt&quot;&gt;企业的热门玩法之一，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;P2P&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt&quot;&gt;行业普遍乐于介入其他领域，尤其是线下消费领域。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 16.8pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt&quot;&gt;日前，大丰收金融在深圳宣布与周&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.ebrun.com/label/co/lukfook.html&quot; title=&quot;六福&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 98, 176);&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;六福&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt&quot;&gt;展开合作。具体的合作方式是，大丰收金融将在周六福的全国线下销售网点开设金融理财体验厅，布局&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;O2O&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt&quot;&gt;线下消费支付版块，周六福还将为大丰收金融的单个借款项目提供质押物回购保证。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin: 8.4pt 0cm 7.8pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 16.8pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt&quot;&gt;根据协议，未来大丰收金融将有望在周六福大陆地区的近&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;1500&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt&quot;&gt;家加盟店及直营店开设金融理财体验厅。与实力&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;P2P&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt&quot;&gt;平台开设直营线下体验门店相比，大丰收金融则是借由传统珠宝连锁店布局线下&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;020&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt&quot;&gt;，由此也吹响了大丰收金融进军线下消费支付版块的&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;“&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt&quot;&gt;号角&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt&quot;&gt;。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin: 8.4pt 0cm 7.8pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 16.8pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt&quot;&gt;大丰收金融总经理谢海青表示，同时注重线上线下需求，此次战略合作旨在&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;“&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt&quot;&gt;吸纳用户与流量，并连接线下实体产品和服务提供商，构建泛销售圈和泛消费圈，而后基于平台用户大数据基础上，打通消费端、产品端、物流端与资金端的链接，为用户打造集理财、消费于一体的生态社区平台，构建无边界互联网金融生态圈。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;”&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin: 8.4pt 0cm 7.8pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 16.8pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt&quot;&gt;传统企业也有意与互联网金融平台合作。出身于金融业的周六福珠宝掌舵者李伟柱董事长在发布会上表示：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;“&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt&quot;&gt;珠宝业属于资金密集型产业，与金融有着千丝万缕的关系。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;”&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin: 8.4pt 0cm 7.8pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 16.8pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt&quot;&gt;同日，大丰收金融还宣布了与保险企业太平保险的合作，据悉，太平保险有望为大丰收金融的单个借款项目提供履约保证保险。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center; line-height: 30pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot; align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin: 8.4pt 0cm 7.8pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 16.8pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt&quot;&gt;据悉，在国际上，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;P2P&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:\r\n9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt&quot;&gt;平台与银行、保险公司的合作模式早已开启。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;“&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt&quot;&gt;目前所有&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;P2P&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt&quot;&gt;平台与专业保险公司的合作模式，仅对平台会员账户资金安全承保，而对&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;P2P&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt&quot;&gt;平台的单个金融标的实行风险保障，对互联网金融行业和保险行业来说都是先例。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt&quot;&gt;大丰收金融董事长杨汉链表示。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',''),(10,2,'达蒙珠宝电商平台即将11月内测','','','','&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:22.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n2.0;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:#333333&quot;&gt;安徽本地首家珠宝&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;F2C&lt;/span&gt;电商平台——达蒙珠宝电商平台即将11月内侧，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 11pt; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 22pt;&quot;&gt;这个由安徽达蒙狗科技有限公司打造的达蒙珠宝电商平台，将珠宝生产厂商、原材料产地、地面实体店等资源整合，通过移动互联网线上线下方式，降低物流成本，直接普惠消费者。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:22.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n2.0;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:#333333&quot;&gt;据了解，&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;2015&lt;/span&gt;年，全球在&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;B2C&lt;/span&gt;电子商务的收入将达到近&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;1.5&lt;/span&gt;万亿欧元，中国的电子商务收入占&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;GDP&lt;/span&gt;的&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;6.9%&lt;/span&gt;，这组数据说明互联网电子商务在交易中扮演重要角色。目前的珠宝消费中呈现线上交易远低于传统实体珠宝店，但随着&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;80&lt;/span&gt;后、&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;90&lt;/span&gt;后开始成为珠宝消费的主流人群后，珠宝电商正以平均每年&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;20%&lt;/span&gt;速度在发展，珠宝线上交易成了一种发展趋势。诚如安徽达蒙狗科技有限公司董事长、安徽珠宝协会常务理事主席徐恒先生提到的：“抓住互联网&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt;的发展机遇，打造&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;F2C&lt;/span&gt;珠宝交易模式回报消费者更多实惠。”&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:22.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n2.0;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:#333333&quot;&gt;何为&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;F2C&lt;/span&gt;模式，安徽达蒙狗科技有限公司&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;CEO&lt;/span&gt;黄杰先生解释到：“&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;F2C&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;即从工厂到消费者，指的是厂商直接面向消费者，产品可以直接从生产线送到消费者手中。由于减少了中间的渠道商这一环节，减少了利润分成，在提高质量保证的同时，让到消费者手中的商品性价比更高，真正做到了回馈于消费者，服务于消费者。”&lt;span style=&quot;color:#333333&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:22.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n2.0;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:#333333&quot;&gt;这种新的营销模式，对传统珠宝行业，对批发、零售业行业都是一次巨大的冲击。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a name=&quot;_GoBack&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',''),(10,1,'达蒙珠宝电商平台即将9月内侧','','','','&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',''),(15,1,'从光棍节到一台戏：双11怎么被“玩坏”的','','','','&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',''),(12,2,'1-7月安徽网上零售额60.8亿 位居中部第二','','','','&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin: 8.4pt 0cm 7.8pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 16.8pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt&quot;&gt;安徽人不仅爱网购，网上销售做得也越来越好。省统计局昨日发布的数据显示，今年&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;1~7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt&quot;&gt;月份，安徽省限额以上批发零售业实现网上商品零售额&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;60.8&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9.5pt;font-fa