-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;据了解，阿里巴巴和苏宁云商将携手整合双方优势资源，利用大数据、物联网、移动应用、金融支付等手段打造O2O移动应用产品，创新O2O运营模式：双方将尝试打通线上线下渠道，苏宁云商辐射全国的1600多家线下门店、3000多家售后服务网点、5000个加盟服务商以及下沉到四五线城市的服务站将与阿里巴巴强大的线上体系实现无缝对接。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;点评：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;老大与老三联合，将直接威胁老二京东&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;的相关业务，电商格局面临新的洗牌。关键是阿里只是想联合吗?想想银泰吧!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;3、京东43亿元投资永辉获一成股份&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;8月7日，京东集团宣布与&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;永辉超市达成战略合作，战略入股永辉超市。根据双方协议，京东入股永辉超市的价格为每股9元(约1.45美元)，总价值为43.1亿元(约7亿美元)。京东商城创始人刘强东以及京东商城副总裁孙加明二人控股的两家子公司将持有永辉超市10%股权，从而成为永辉超市的第三大股东。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;随后，永辉在公告中表示，双方合作主要涉及四大方面：强化联盟协同、积极探索线上线下合作模式及O2O业务发展、仓储物流协作，以及共同挖掘互联网金融资源。双方将建立高层定期沟通机制，共同商议合作重大事项。永辉的非公开发行股票预案同时提到，“京东强大的物流能力为消费者带来良好的购物体验，未来双方将积极探索在仓储、物流、系统、人员等方面的融合。”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;据悉，今年以来京东在大力发展生活服务O2O市场，并设立独立全资子公司“京东到家”，提供的服务项目包括3公里范围内生鲜、超市产品、鲜花、外卖送餐等服务。目前京东到家开启的城市为：北京、上海、广州、深圳，京东宣称北上广的日均最高订单量超过5万单。京东到家采取的是众包模式。为此，分析人士认为，京东到家可与永辉超市有很好的结合。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;点评：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;京东觊觎生鲜已久，但都没有找到好方法，联合永辉走生鲜O2O或有可能，对永辉而言也是瞌睡遇着枕头，毕竟永辉的电商之路一直都不顺。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;4、沃尔玛&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;全吞1号店&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;7月13日，沃尔玛全球高管到达中国召集1号店高层开会宣布，1号店联合创始人——董事长于刚与CEO刘峻岭已经离职。随后，7月23日，沃尔玛宣布从中国平安&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;以及1号店前董事长于刚、前CEO刘峻岭手中购买了1号店余下股份，全资拥有1号店在中国的电子商务&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;业务，并将委任沃尔玛全球电子商务亚洲区总裁王路将执掌1号店。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://iddmall.com/image/catalog/xinwen/01.08/1-2.png&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;沃尔玛官方公告称，在全资控股1号店后，沃尔玛计划投资加速电商业务的发展，希望为线上、移动端和实体店的顾客创造无缝联接的购物体验。同时，1号店将会继续以现有名称运营，并将继续保持本土领导的团队。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;而于刚和刘峻岭在离开1号店之后，运作医药电商壹药网谋求东山再起。资料显示，壹药网被1号店收购后，2014年从1号店剥离。于刚也表示，未来还将打通医院资源，利用互联网技术以及可穿戴设备，为消费者提供医、药、健康等完整的解决方案，让在线问诊和线上买药成为用户习惯。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;点评：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;早在推出大卖场O2O服务平台“速购”时，沃尔玛对电商的野心就凸显出来。但电商业务与线下大卖场业务的相互分离，就注定即使全资控股，二者之间要协调平衡仍任重道远。至于1号店会不会走向没落，也未可知。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;5、万达&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;“抛弃”零售业&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;2015年7月，万达（专题阅读）集团宣布旗下80多家大歌星KTV全面退出KTV领域，或被转让，或改变成餐饮、商铺等其他业态。数据显示，去年上半年大歌星新开业5家店，累计开业86家店，整体收入仅为4.04亿元。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;万达商管公司总裁曲德君也承认，受国家行业相关政策影响，连锁经营KTV的利润十分微薄，已不太适合万达这样规模的企业经营。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;此外，今年7月，万达集团下发文件，除年初关闭的10家门店外，万达百货将继续关闭济南、唐山、江门、温州、荆州等多个地区共40余家严重亏损的门店，包括上海宝山、泉州、襄阳等地区的个别门店也将进行调整，压缩经营面积。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;资料显示，万达百货去年完成收入154.9亿元，同比增长39%，只完成调整后计划的91%。万达百货净利润增亏7%，亏损依旧不断扩大。此大规模“关店”意在集中处理亏损严重的门店，以及希望引入更多的体验式业态来提高万达的流量和营业额。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;曲德君也强调，万达百货和大歌星KTV的调整也事关万达整体战略转型，万达集团正在进行企业的第四次转型，就是要调整一些传统产业，向更有发展前景的文化、旅游、体育等产业转型。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;点评：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;王健林一向很现实，不赚钱的业务要来干嘛?万达的负债率一直很高，难道也有卖店还债的打算?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;6、蓝月亮“大战”KA卖场&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;今年6月，蓝月亮的产品在广州、成都、西安等地的大润发&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;、人人乐&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;、家乐福&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;等大型超市下架;7月10日，商超渠道危机进一步升级，随着与家乐福的谈判失败，蓝月亮产品在北京家乐福超市全线下架。由于宣称要自建电商渠道，摆脱对传统大卖场的依赖，蓝月亮一度与零售商的关系十分紧张。蓝月亮总裁罗秋平表示，下架风波是因为在推新品过程中与部分卖场没有达成一致，“我们要推浓缩洗衣液需要足够的展台和消费者近距离沟通，而一些卖场并不认同我们的做法。”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;大润发此前也发布声明表示，“蓝月亮不想做卖场的进货商，想做专柜售卖，不符合大润发商品陈列制度，目前全部蓝月亮商品已经下架。”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;分析人士认为，蓝月亮要着力发展线上渠道。目前，蓝月亮线上分销体系分别是建立自营平台月亮商城、微商城月亮小屋，和入驻京东、天猫&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;、1号店等大流量电商平台。此外，为了配合线上，垂直整合了线下资源，蓝月亮和社区洗涤店展开广泛合作，物流配送方面除了和第三方配送团队合作之外还建立了社区清洁顾问，只为解决产品最终的销售问题。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;点评：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;其实快消品想要拓展渠道无可厚非，但线上渠道的营销费用又比线下少多少呢?还不是一样各种广告各种促销活动。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;7、顺丰&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;嘿客又变成顺丰家会顺吗？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;5月18日，在嘿客成立一年之际，顺丰宣布将此O2O项目升级为顺丰家，和之前的嘿客相比，顺丰家门店功能区分类更细化，购物功能更便捷。店内商品展示区分为当季美食专区、全球直采专区、母婴海淘专区、新鲜到家专区以及会员专区等。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://iddmall.com/image/catalog/xinwen/01.08/1-3.png&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;据悉，现在的顺丰家更多地集中在物流和服务两大功能上，嘿客原先的商品销售功能已经被更多地看作线上超市顺丰优选&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;的延伸。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;虽然顺丰否认失败，但外界普遍认为这是嘿客失败的象征。对此，顺丰公关部负责人回应称，门店优化是实体连锁行业的常态机制，顺丰商业根据整体市场情况也在逐步优化嘿客门店的的社区布局。顺丰将持续拓展社区渠道建设，今年仍然会陆续开业新的线下社区店。同时，部分嘿客门店逐步升级为顺丰家，是为了更好地贴近社区提升社区用户体验，且在很长一段时间内，嘿客和顺丰家将同时存在。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;据了解，顺丰家的此次升级，目的在于突出社区服务功能，致力于扩展为用户提供生活速递类，免费便民类及私人定制类等服务功能。通过将线下的顺丰家、顺丰嘿客与线上的顺丰优选联合，将努力打造一个&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;线上线下一体的购物平台。顺丰也逐渐从最初的物流商的定位拓展，走向物流、电商、服务三位一体的定位。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;点评：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;从快递到零售，顺丰一直在试错，说不定顺丰家也是个试验品。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;8、百果园融资4亿元&amp;nbsp;将催化行业整合&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;